################
# TOP
################
top

# h - help
# W - save config in file ~/.topc
# View:
#		V - process tree
# 	c - full path for process
# 	t - change style for results CPU (in header)
# 	m - change style for results MEMORY (in header)
# 	d - change refresh interval (could use 0.1)
# 	z - highlight
# Sort:
# 	P - sort by CPU Utilization
# 	M - sort by Memory
#		T - sort by running time
#		N - sort by process ID
# Filter:
# 	u - user
# 	o - filter (example: COMMAND=docker, !COMMAND=atom, %CPU>3.0)
# Action:
# 	k - kill process
